name: hypnotoad
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "hypnotoad" %}
{% set version = "0.4.3" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 65f348bfa85f6e8e018897a8b4b8cb36d5af8ed85d3cda73adb740a5dabfe515

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  entry_points:
    - hypnotoad_circular = hypnotoad.scripts.hypnotoad_circular:main
    - hypnotoad_geqdsk = hypnotoad.scripts.hypnotoad_geqdsk:main
    - hypnotoad_torpex = hypnotoad.scripts.hypnotoad_torpex:main
    - hypnotoad-gui = hypnotoad.gui:main

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - boututils >=0.1.7
    - dill >=0.3
    - func_timeout >=4.3
    - matplotlib-base >=3.2
    - netcdf4 >=1.5
    - numpy >=1.18
    - optionsfactory >=1.0.3
    - pyparsing >=2.4
    - pyyaml >=5.1
    - scipy >=1.6
    - qt.py >=1.2
  run_constrained:
    - pyside2 >=5.13
    - pyqt >=5.12

test:
  requires:
    - pytest
    - pyside2
  commands:
    - pytest --pyargs hypnotoad
    - hypnotoad_circular -h
    - hypnotoad_geqdsk -h
    - hypnotoad_torpex -h
    - hypnotoad-gui -h

about:
  home: https://github.com/boutproject/hypnotoad
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENCE
  summary: Python grid generator for BOUT++
  dev_url: https://github.com/boutproject/hypnotoad

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - johnomotani
    - ZedThree
